write Wiki Pages:

--- Overview ---
Home (Description, Main Features, based on Steam Audio tech, Acknowledgements)
Installation (Asset Lib or GitHub, activate Plugin, Troubleshooting: multiple GDExtensions)
Getting Started (Project Setup, minimal scene: Runtime, ProbeVolume, Geometry, Player)

--- Core Nodes ---
ResonanceRuntime and RuntimeConfig (listener updates, quality, HRTF, occlusion, reflections, pathing)
ResonancePlayer and PlayerConfig (occlusion, directivity, pathing_probe_volume, perspective)
ResonanceListener (listener position, debug viz)
ResonanceProbeVolume and BakeConfig (probe layout, bake_config, bake_sources, bake_listeners)
ResonanceStaticGeometry and ResonanceDynamicGeometry (geometry_override, export)
ResonanceStaticScene (container for exported static scene assets)
ResonanceMaterial (absorption, scattering, transmission; presets)

--- Bake Workflow ---
Bake Workflow (order: Probes → Pathing → Static Source/Listener; toolbar buttons; BakeConfig params)
Probe/Runtime Compatibility (baked_reflection_type vs runtime; pathing_enabled vs pathing baked)

--- Audio Features ---
ResonanceAudioEffect (reverb bus, auto-configured)
ResonanceSOFAAsset and SOFA Import (custom HRTF from .sofa files)
ResonanceAmbisonicPlayer (Ambisonics with HRTF decode)

--- Configuration ---
Project Settings (audio/nexus_resonance/logger/*)
Audio Buffer and Latency (audio_frame_size, output latency)

--- Editor ---
Editor Tools (Toolbar: Export Static Scene, Export Dynamic Meshes, Bake All, Clear, Unlink Probe Refs; Gizmo)

--- Debug ---
Debug and Visualization (Debug overlay, occlusion/reflection/path rays, ResonanceLogger)

--- Reference ---
ResonanceMaterial Presets (concrete, wood, metal, glass, brick, drywall, plaster, carpet, fabric, rubber, plastic, ceramic, marble tile, acoustic ceiling tile, gravel/sand, water)
Known Issues (Probe Volume deletion refs, dynamic mesh export; from docs/ISSUES.md)

--- Community ---
Contributing (build from source, setup, tests; from docs/CONTRIBUTING.md)
